# Design Document

## Overview

**{{title}}**

{{description}}

This design restructures {{componentName}} while preserving its externally
observable behavior. That preservation is a claim to be verified, not
assumed: the plan pins behavior with tests first, then restructures in
checkpointed steps, and measures what a "pure" refactor can still change —
performance, timing, and error messages.

